description: Gonzo Gourmet offers fresh street food with a gourmet twist. Items include a signature Hot Chicken, which is spicy fried modeled after popular Nashville joints. Menu varies but also can include Outlaw Eggs Benedict, Tacos al Pastor, Gyros, Bacon-Wrapped Hot Dogs, Avocado Tacos, Chipotle Black Bean Burgers, Hashbrown Casserole, and many more. Gonzo strives to use local ingredients and offers a fun tasty experience for all customers.
name: Gonzo Gourmet
